title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Megabucks' game
maintext:
PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the Oregon Lottery’s “Megabucks” game were:
17-19-24-28-34-36
(seventeen, nineteen, twenty-four, twenty-eight, thirty-four, thirty-six)
Estimated jackpot: $2 million
